OL,5,C` ABI
OL,7,FWeather damage was not just a problem
OL,8,Ffor homeowners, with businesses
OL,9,Fincurring #443 million in weather
OL,10,Fclaims in 2023.
OL,12,FThe average weather-related payout for
OL,13,Fbusinesses last year was #18,542,
OL,14,Fjumping from #12,612 in 2022.
OL,16,FThe ABI said that property insurers
OL,17,Fhad typically paid out around #13
OL,18,Fmillion per day last year to help
OL,19,Fhomeowners and businesses cope with
OL,20,Fevents including flooding and theft.
