OL,7,FThe industry paid out #4.86 billion to
OL,8,Fhomeowners and businesses in 2023, the
OL,9,FABI said.
OL,11,FMore than half of this figure ` #2.55
OL,12,Fbillion ` was for home insurance
OL,13,Fclaims.
OL,15,FThe ABI said this total was up from
OL,16,F#2.33 billion in 2022 and was driven
OL,17,Fby weather-related damage.
