OL,7,FWhile the total number of claims
OL,8,Fremained fairly level, the average
OL,9,Fclaim paid to businesses and
OL,10,Fhomeowners rose to #6,235, an 11%
OL,11,Fincrease compared with 2022.
OL,13,FLouise Clark, policy adviser at the
OL,14,FABI said: "Extreme weather events may
OL,15,Fnot feel so rare as they used to as we
OL,16,Fgrapple with a changing climate.
